§ 737. Repealed. Pub. L. 117–263, div. K, title CXVIII, § 11808(a)(8), Dec. 23, 2022, 136 Stat. 4165
Section, act May 14, 1908, ch. 168, § 4, 35 Stat. 162, as affected by act June 17, 1910, ch. 301, § 6, 36 Stat. 538, related to maintenance of anchorage buoys in New York and Philadelphia harbors. See section 548 of Title 14, Coast Guard.
